---
title: Cheerful Chorizo and Black Bean Frejolada with Pickled Red Onion, Soured Cream and Coriander
description: Just like Britain, Peru loves its beans, which they call 'frijoles'! That's where frejolada, this wholesome and warming bean stew, gets its name from. It's finished with a sprinkling of fresh coriander, onion pickle and cooling soured cream for a flavour adventure.
